{"title":"母亲（外一首）","authors":["陈太顺"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈太顺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲搓草绳的手艺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴许是在她年轻编辫子时就学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她0搓草绳的动作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就和她编辫子一样优美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院的篱笆是草绳编织的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄瓜架是草绳牵联的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄芽白是草绳捆扎的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便在冬天  母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在腰里系一根草绳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲搓草绳时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是唱长长的歌谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把月光唱得铮亮铮亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把孩子的眼睛唱得铮圆铮圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸着山珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩满一天星光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲用不起眼的草绳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捆住一个农家的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院不会松散"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子不会暗淡"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}